job_history.work_description: Greets members, maintains place organized, and maintains friendly environment. Works with retail, advertises products, and restocks shelves as needed. Resolves member's troubles, and answers phone inquiries. Completes agreements with incoming members.

Partners up with businesses surrounding 24 Hour Fitness to create member traffic. Promotes company special promotions. Completes agreements and manages daily paperwork. Successfully attains personal and company revenue target.
Organized inventory (FIFO method). Met weekly deadlines for inventory, and members' financial transactions. Organized banking information for POS system.
